bilingual.source: The government is warning people about falling rocks.
bilingual.target: 政府正在警告人们注意落石。

bilingual.source: Annie called out a warning to the captain above the sound of the storm.
bilingual.target: 安妮在风暴的声音中向船长发出警告。

bilingual.source: Magma building up can be a warning sign that a volcano is getting ready to erupt.
bilingual.target: 岩浆积聚可能是火山即将喷发的警告信号。

bilingual.source: He chose to disregard the warning signs.
The police officer fired a warning shot.
bilingual.target: 警察开了一枪警告射击。
他愚蠢地忽视了警告信号。

bilingual.source: It is foolish to ignore the warning signs.
bilingual.target: 忽视警告信号是愚蠢的。

bilingual.source: Please heed the warning signs on the road.
bilingual.target: 请注意路上的警告标志。

list.abstract: GREEN DAY的 新专辑《warning》，有十三首歌曲。
《warning》是日本女子偶像组合AKB48的专辑《Team A 3rd stage “谁かのために” ~studio recordings コレクション~》里的单曲。

yingyinNormal.en: Let this be a warning to the world.
What are they? What the stone was warning me about.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它们是什么？正是宝石警告我的东西。

yingyinNormal.en: They have detected the message warning them to protect themselves.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它们收到了警告袭击来临的信息，随后 它们也开启了防卫机制。

yingyinNormal.en: Which is kind of a big deal. Of course I could let you off with a warning if you were to glove those trunks.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这也不是小事了，当然如果你肯戴上我是可以给你个警告了事。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, no, it's just, I'm just warning you, you know, if you find yourself 3,000 miles away and craving a hit of this, you know I can't Skype it to you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，我只是警告你，当你发现自己在五千公里之外渴望得到这诱人的身躯，我不能通过视频给你。

yingyinNormal.en: Sheldon, I'm warning you, I can play this game, too. If it's like your 3-D chess game, then you're out of your length, width and depth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿，我警告你，你玩的小把戏的我也会玩。如果你玩小把戏和玩三维象棋的水准一样，那你可是在三个维度上都不自量力。

yingyinNormal.en: I just can't believe that Mike didn't give me any warning.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我真不明白，为什么他不给我点暗示。

yingyinNormal.en: A nearby cell sees the warning and immediately goes into action.
yingyinNormal.zh: 旁边一个细胞看到了这个警示，立刻开始行动。

yingyinNormal.en: Just warning you. I'm gonna go right. Don't make a big deal out of it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 提醒你下，这次我要弄右边，不要大惊小怪哦。

yingyinNormal.en: He doesn't usually go against my advice without giving me fair warning.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他一般不会招呼都不打，就违背我的建议。

yingyinNormal.en: Word of warning page 73. I don't understand. It makes no sense. It looks impossible.
yingyinNormal.zh: 提醒一下，是第73页的。我完全不明白，说不通啊，不可能啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Your honor, this bullet is clearly a warning of violence to come to Mrs. Ruiz and her family.
yingyinNormal.zh: 法官阁下，这枚子弹无疑是对鲁伊兹夫人及其家人的暴力威胁。

yingyinNormal.en: Fair warning, we can get crazy. Yeah. Last week we smoked cigars and pretended to be dragons.
yingyinNormal.zh: 友情提示: 我们会变得很疯狂的哦。是呀，上周我们抽了雪茄，还假装自己是龙呢。

yingyinNormal.en: Word of warning, though. I'm prone to night terrors so when I wake up kicking and screaming, don't panic.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不过，温馨提示，我有夜惊倾向，所以如果我睁眼乱踢或尖叫，别慌。

yingyinNormal.en: M's idea? Precisely. Oh, one word of warning. The alarm is rather loud. If you know what I mean. I think I do.
yingyinNormal.zh: M的主意吗？正是，要提醒你下，闹钟声音挺响的，你要是懂我意思的话。明白。

yingyinNormal.en: Fair warning, may be working out some anger issues on the racquetball court this morning. Don't ask. Sounds good.
yingyinNormal.zh: 说明一下，今早的壁球训练我可能要发泄一下情绪，别问原因。没问题。

yingyinNormal.en: Authorities in San Francisco are attributing a tremendous amount of lives saved, thanks to local experts, who were able to give ample warning of the massive quake.
yingyinNormal.zh: 以及旧金山政府对那位专家致以衷心的感谢，正是因为他及时向大众发出地震预警从而拯救了无数人的生命。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: The Food Standards Authority has issued a public <highlight>warning</highlight> about the risks of a compound called acrylamide that forms in some foods cooked at high temperatures.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 食品标准局就一种名为丙烯酰胺的化合物的危险发出公开警告，该化合物在一些高温烹调的食物中形成。

examination_example.sentence: France's planned tax is a clear <highlight>warning</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 法国计划征税是一个明确的警告。

examination_example.sentence: Today is no different, with academics, writers, and activists once again <highlight>warning</highlight> that technology is replacing human workers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 今天也不例外，学者、作家和活动人士再次警告说，技术正在取代人类工人。
